query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('apache2',
'ef-code-first',
'fork',
'gulp',
'hosting',
'html-lists',
'linq-to-entities',
'many-to-many',
'nodes',
'overloading',
'permutation',
'protocols',
'signals',
'visual-studio-2008',
'word-vba');
